{"id":"entities/cs-461","title":"CS 461 (OSU Software Engineering capstone)","type":"entities","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>Stub. <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">OSU</a> senior software-engineering capstone sequence. Yahir's group (Group 27, with <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/bryant-shitabata\">Bryant</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/jacob-cocheu\">Jacob</a>, <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/sonny-box\">Sonny</a>) built the <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/baby-tracking-app\">privacy friendly baby tracking app</a> PRD'd in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-12-04-requirements-document-2\">2024 12 04 requirements document 2</a>. The \"final class\" referenced in <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2023-09-05-todo-82423\">the Aug 2023 todo</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Connections: <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"entities/osu\">osu</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/cs-coursework\">cs coursework</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"summaries/2024-12-04-requirements-document-2\">2024 12 04 requirements document 2</a> · <a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/baby-tracking-app\">baby tracking app</a></p>\n","related":[{"id":"entities/bryant-shitabata","label":"Bryant Shitabata"},{"id":"summaries/2025-04-23-screenshot-2025-04-23-at-9-41-21-am-93084ac1","label":"CS 461 — Ubuntu i386 libreadline fix for `access` binary"},{"id":"summaries/2024-12-04-requirements-document-2","label":"CS 461 Privacy-Friendly Baby Tracking App PRD (12/4/24)"},{"id":"summaries/2024-01-06-CS-492-Syllabus","label":"CS 492 Syllabus — Mobile Software Development"},{"id":"concepts/cs-coursework","label":"CS Coursework"},{"id":"entities/jacob-cocheu","label":"Jacob Cocheu"},{"id":"entities/osu","label":"Oregon State University (OSU)"},{"